Amy Sedaris https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Amy_Sedaris 0 Amy Louise Sedaris (; born March 29, 1961) is an American actress, comedian and writer known for playing Jerri Blank in the Comedy Central television series Strangers with Candy. She regularly collaborates with her older brother David, a humorist and author. Since 2014, Sedaris has voiced the character Princess Carolyn in the Netflix animated series BoJack Horseman.
